Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Dr. David R. Hawkins. I'm a physician, psychiatrist, psychoanalyst, nutritionist.\NI've been doing research in the nature of consciousness itself and levels of awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that the world calls spiritual. Out of this, plus my 35 years of clinical experience, as well as my\Nown personal experience, we've derived knowledge that can be extremely useful in alleviating
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,human suffering in all its forms, many of which I've lived through in my own personal life,\Nand I've been forced to find answers that are outside the field of traditional medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:01:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about, in this particular workshop today, pain and suffering, the alleviation of pain\Nand suffering. To begin with, that the world thinks that they are the same thing. To get off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the idea and to show how to separate that suffering is one thing and pain is another.\NTo look at the world as a whole, as a whole, as a whole, as a whole, as a whole, as a whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to look into what it means, physical, mental, and spiritual. It is said that all diseases,\Nall illnesses, all human problems are physical, mental, and spiritual. What does that actually
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,mean? As a physician, I've learned all about the physical. As a psychiatrist, about the mental.\NAnd in consciousness and spiritual work, about the spiritual dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is meant by spirit? Is this a fantasy? Is it something real? Is it something we can\Nwork with? Is it something that's only useful for religious people? What do we need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,about that, that we can experience the truth of for ourself? How can we utilize this knowledge\Nfor the alleviation of our own problems and of those that we love?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we'll be talking about how to handle acute pain, how to handle chronic pain,\Nhow to handle the pain itself, and even more importantly, how to be with that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we have two different things to address. One is the problem itself, the symptoms,\Nhow to handle them specifically. And there we'll also be looking at such things as
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the use of hypnosis and acupuncture, what part do they play in alleviation of pain.\NAnd we'll be looking at levels of consciousness. In other words, how to be with that experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,how to be with the experience.\NOf that problem, and the problem, of course, we're looking at today, is that of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And in going into that, we'll be utilizing a map of consciousness, which we have evolved\Nas a composite of many fields of endeavor and joint study that I've done with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you'll see on the blackboard, we have something that we'll be referring to that is\Nextremely useful and we've found very helpful. And that is sort of a mathematical model
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of the levels of consciousness. They've been calibrated as to their relative power, the\Ndirection of their energy fields, what the emotional component is, what the process going
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on in consciousness is, how that influences our view of the world, and our view of a God\Nif we have one. And if we don't have one, what does that come out of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll be addressing clinical examples, things that I've experienced,\Nthrough myself, even recently in my own personal life, so that I can attest to the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they work.\NThey work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They've worked for me.\NThey've worked for others who've tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They've worked clinically.\NAnd out of this experience we demonstrate certain principles of consciousness which
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,have a benefit to our life as a whole, to our life as a whole.\NWhat we learn in studying one specific problem then generalizes to our life as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll be turning lemons into lemonade, how to turn something that the world considers\Nto be awful, such as pain, how to derive benefit from that, how to have your life prosper as
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a result of what you've learned from this one specific incidence.\NWe need to know something about what is the nature of consciousness itself, and from that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll learn a lot that will help us in our life in general.\NWhat is the nature of human experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is experience?\NWhat is experience experienced?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So to begin with, we'll look at the relationship between body, mind, and spirit.\NWhat does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it besides just a catchphrase?\NEverybody says body, mind, and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?\NWhat is it practically?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself came, you know, as a scientist with a skeptical, pragmatic mind.\NI'm very impressed by what works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very unimpressed by.\NThe hypothetical and the theoretical.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very interested in what brings about results and what you can reduplicate through your\Nown experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be sharing my personal experience, my clinical experience, and the results of\Nour research.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll look at the relationship between mind, body, and spirit, and how these are\Nexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing to realize is that the body has no capacity to experience itself.\NThis is a surprising thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we think we're experiencing our body.\NWe all think we are our body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the body get experienced?\NWell, the arm, for instance, has no way of experiencing its armness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The leg cannot experience its own being a leg.\NIt's because these parts are experienced through sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So sensations of the body is what we're experiencing.\NWe're not experiencing the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're experiencing our sensations of the body.\NAnd where are these sensations of the body being?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they being?\NThey're being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're being experienced in the mind.\NWithout a mind, you cannot experience what is going on in the body, the sensations that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,are telling us about the body.\NAnd so experiences going on then of the body is occurring in the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your experience of your body is not occurring in your body.\NIt's occurring in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first surprising thought to get used to.\NThe next surprising thought is that mind cannot experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The next surprising thought is it not.\NA thought cannot experience its own thoughtness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A feeling cannot experience its own feelingness.\NA memory cannot experience its own memoryness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind itself has to be in something greater than itself in order to know what is going\Non in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know what is going on in your mind?\NYou know what's going on in your mind because of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So mind itself and the content of mind, what's going on in mind, is not going to be in the mind.\NIt's going to be in the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is being known through consciousness\Nso that all experience is occurring then in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your awareness of what is happening\Nis occurring within your consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We know this if, for instance, you cut a part of the brain\Nso that a part of the mind is no longer operative
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in the physical domain.\NIf you cut part of the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then the opposite side of the body, let's say,\Nis no longer experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, body is experienced in mind,\Nno mind, no experience of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that if you eliminate consciousness,\Nthere is no awareness of what is going on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the whole purpose of anesthesia.\NThe purpose of anesthesia is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,when you cut out consciousness,\Nthere is no awareness of what is going on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Interestingly, consciousness itself\Nis experienced from an even greater domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as this progresses,\Nyou get that the lesser is always experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,from that which is the greater.\NIt is the greater that encompasses
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and allows the experience of the lesser.\NAnd consciousness itself is then experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in the greatest domain,\Nand that is the one without limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,called awareness.\NIt is awareness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the nature of awareness,\Nbeing itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to know,\Nto know what is going on in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the nature of consciousness\Nto know what is going on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the nature of mind\Nto know what is going on with sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the nature of sensations\Nto know what is going on with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the importance of this?\NThe importance of it is to know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that all experience,\Nordinary experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is going on in consciousness alone.\NWhere is consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When we say,\Nwhen we experience something,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where do we experience it?\NIs there a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is consciousness located?\NDoes it have a specific space?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it someplace?\NIt is important for us to know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that consciousness has no space.\NIt has no area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no limitation.\NThe common fantasy is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I experience things in my head.\NActually, you don't experience them in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you experience a thought?\NYou are experiencing a thought nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no specific space\Nin which you are experiencing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing thought.\NThe nature of consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that it has no particular form.\NConsciousness is without form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Its content is with form.\NBut the field of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is like space,\Nhaving no particular locality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be important to us later today\Nas we discuss
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the techniques of handling pain.\NBecause pain can be handled
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,both locally and generally.\NSo we have several ways
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in which now we are going to\Nbe approaching the handling of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How to handle the specific sensation.\NHow to handle the experience of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And how to handle\Nand be with that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as you exist, as you are,\Nthe way you as a being are
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with that experience of that pain.\NAnd how you have evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in your own consciousness\Nwill determine whether the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,involves suffering or not.\NIsn't that a surprising thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That pain is one thing,\Nand suffering is another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first thing we want to\Nget rid of in our minds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is the belief system\Nthat pain is therefore suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that sets up\Na whole series of programs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which we are going to need to undo.\NPain is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is quite possible to be with pain\Nand be totally indifferent to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible for pain to exist in the body\Nand to have relatively little or no experience
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of that pain.\NNo suffering about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have ever had surgery,\Nfor instance, and have had anesthesia,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,have had analgesia,\Nis the better term.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, an injection of Demerol or something\Nwill know that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you've had a gallbladder attack,\Nlet's say, or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've had analgesic,\Nwill know that in that state
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain is still there.\NThe pain exists on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you as a being are no longer\Nsuffering about that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the pain is there,\Nand you are here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:12:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are not necessarily connected\Nwith that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain exists on its own,\Nbut without you being at the effect of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's not necessary\Nto be the victim of the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One can be with it in such a way\Nthat the pain is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am with that pain\Nin a way that does not involve suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,does not involve\Nany kind of agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To realize that that is possible\Nis the first step
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that leads us out of it.\NLetting go of the belief
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that pain and suffering are the same thing.\NAnd today in this we'll talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact is,\Nis going to the dentist necessarily painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, no.\NAt one time in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,going to the dentist was agonizing.\NIt took a handful of pills
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and tranquilizers,\Nand this is many, many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remember I would\Nput off going because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,my pain threshold was so low\NI literally had to have analgesia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to get my teeth cleaned.\NAnd my pain threshold was so low
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that I was pain prone.\NSo we'll be talking today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,about pain proneness.\NWhat is it that sets our pain threshold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that sets our readiness\Nto experience pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the years went by\Nand I learned these various
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual techniques\Nand consciousness techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and began to apply them,\Nthe experience of pain began to diminish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Much to my surprise,\NI could go to the dentist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and experience moderate pain\Ninstead of agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the pain became mild.\NThen it only became a discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I go to the dentist now\NI don't even notice any discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm in the chair for a minute\Nand I'm out and I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are you done already?\NI can hardly believe you're done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we get to near the end of the tape\Nwe'll discuss some perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,self-hypnotic techniques\Nto reinforce what we've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be utilizing that\Nsort of auto-suggestion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to reinforce what we've learned.\NHow to utilize a somewhat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,altered state of consciousness\Nin your own behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How to come from a suggestible space\Nto learn more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to relieve pain.\NWe'll be talking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as a means of quickly\Neducating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've got to go to the dentist next week\Nyou don't have much time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to learn the techniques.\NAnd we'll learn some ways
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to speed them up.\NFirst thing we want to address ourselves to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is the handling of acute pain.\NYou're walking along
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly you sprain your ankle\Nand the pain is agonizing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or you break your leg\Nor you suddenly have a gallbladder attack
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or renal colic\Nor a coronary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or just an ordinary accident\Nor you bark your shin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you hit your head on something.\NHow to handle that acute situation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,will reveal to us a technique\Nthat we'll be utilizing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the series\Nin healing a variety of illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and a way of utilizing it\Nin healing both acute and chronic pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's start with acute pain.\NThe sudden shock
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of suddenly finding yourself\Nyou've had an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've scalded yourself.\NYou've poured hot water on your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've burned yourself\Non the sink or the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a technique\Nthat we're going to get a lot of mileage out of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is the whole concept\Nof letting go resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to look at\Nwhat is the benefit in letting go resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and compare it to what mind ordinarily does.\NWhat mind ordinarily does
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is resist an experience.\NIt resists it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the expectation of suffering.\NIt has a program already set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain means suffering\Nand I'm going to resist this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fantasy is\Nthat if I resist it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will eliminate it.\NSo the first thing we have to know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the relief of pain and suffering\Ncomes rapidly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,by going 180 degrees\Nin the opposite direction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is by letting go resisting the pain\Nand we'll talk about exactly how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll use some clinical examples\Nof rapid healing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that come about\Nthrough a completely different technique
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,than is used by the mind\Nin an average situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting go resistance\Nis a process
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that takes place\Nin everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go resistance means\Nto be with the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and totally surrender\Nto the sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It means to ignore the thoughts\Nthat you may be having about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of thinking about it\Nyou go right into the direct experience
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sensation\Nand you totally let go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you burn yourself by accident.\NAt first it will be like an overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like\Nyou ask for more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You let the doors open\Nand the pain rushes in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and you totally surrender to it\Nand let go resisting to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact the way to do this\Nis to say more, more, more, more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way to hold this in mind\Nso that this is acceptable to you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is to know that there is only so much pain\Nin any experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be like let's say\Nit's a 50 pound pain experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You open the door to it\Nand you let the whole 49 pounds of it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,run out rapidly.\NSo I let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this experience.\NI let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,being with it.\NI ignore the thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because the thoughts are not going to be useful.\NInstead I totally surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I allow myself\Nto experience it totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens then\Nis it's like the door is open
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a rush.\NIt's like I'm going to be experienced out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in a very rapid few minutes.\NI remember twisting my ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in San Francisco\Nand it was a severe twist
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that ordinarily would have put you\Nyou would have ended up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing the orthopedist\Nand getting your ankle taped
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or maybe even a cast put on\Nfor say six weeks or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead what I did\Nis I sat down on the park bench
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just closed my eyes\Nand I surrendered to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in waves of excruciating pain.\NIf I had resisted it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have ended up in a cast.\NIn other words it turns an acute
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,into a chronic condition\Nif you resist it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens is I sat down on the park bench\Nand I just let it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,swamp over me.\NI just surrendered to it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and waves of pain came over me\Nand yet curiously enough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's devoid of suffering.\NWhy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was choosing to experience the experience.\NAnd in doing that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the master of the experience.\NI'm no longer the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that is saying\NI choose to experience it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,give me more of it.\NBecause of that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the amount of suffering involved\Nas you look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is really minimal.\NThe alleviation of the pain is very rapid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would say within\Nthree to four minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was up again and walking.\NAnd now the pain had gone down
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept letting go\Nresisting that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When I broke my left foot\NI did the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke my left foot\Nchopping wood and a huge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,oak log fell on it\Nand crushed all the bones across the front of the foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know by Christmas\NI was dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By Christmas I was back in the ballroom dancing.\NNever had a cast
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,did nothing about it except\Nconsciously choose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go resisting that experience.\NThere was an accidental amputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And again the same thing\Nthe shock of the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and then knowing now\Nhow to handle it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the letting go of resisting\Nthis experience
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the constantly letting go of the sensations\Nletting go resisting these sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you do that\Nwhat the world would call miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,happens right before your eyes.\NAs I let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because I cut this thumb off\Nwith a saw, a circular saw
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing I did is\NI instantly stopped resisting the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just stood still\Nand allowed it to sweep in over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I did that\Nwithin seconds the bleeding stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I literally\NI have the visa board in which this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There is eight drops of blood.\NThere are eight drops of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By letting go resisting the experience\Nthe digital artery which had been cut across
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and should have pulsated\Nin a grotesque kind of fashion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,no such thing happened.\NRoss with whom I have done
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a great deal of this research\Nhad burned herself severely in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And she just stood there\Nand consciously released letting go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that burn\Nand the pain of the burn was gone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in a matter of a minute or two\Nand later there wasn't even a blister there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It should have by rights swollen up\Nto a big water blister
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and taken months to heal.\NAnd the only thing that happened
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,was a discoloration.\NA member of my class did the same
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,thing. He burned both of his hands.\NHe is a woodworker,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a cabinet maker.\NHe burned both his hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:22:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and he followed the same technique.\NInstantly let go resisting that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead of two hands\Nhe should have had two hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,by rights two hands swollen up\Nlike this full of blisters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and should have had his hand in bandages\Nfor weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead in a matter of he said\Nthree or four minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain was gone\Nand there was no formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see an instant healing.\NThe body knows how to heal itself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.29,0:22:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute we let go of resistance.\NNow let's look a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,at why this should be so.\NThere is no magic involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody can experience\Nthe truth of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This has been a common teaching\Nfor thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have ever\Ntried Zen meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,will know that the first thing\Nthey teach you is the handling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of the physical body\Nis to go into that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go of the resisting\Nof the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:23:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and to cancel out thoughts about that\Nto become one with it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and thereby disappear it.\NSo we are doing what in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,work is called disappearing.\NBy totally letting go of the resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of a thing we disappear it.\NWe disappear it out of our experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see experience is prolonged\Nby resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.38,0:23:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as I resist the thing\Nthat gives its existence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,my resistance is what gives it\Nthe power over me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I now become the victim of that.\NI am at the effect of that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which I resist.\NThe minute I let go of my resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,become one with it\NI disappear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we will see the reasons for it.\NI have always been a very left brain person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have learned to enlarge\Nmy right brain capacities.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But for most of us\Nall of these things make more sense
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so we will go over to the blackboard\Nwhere we have this map of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that we referred to before.\NAnd we will look at some energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:24:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in this particular box\Na lot of people
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,who followed our work here\Ncall this the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is in the box\Nare levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.06,0:24:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And these levels of consciousness\Nare labeled according to common
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.06,0:24:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,human experience so that they are understandable.\NEach of these levels
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness\Nhas also been calibrated mathematically
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we can see\Nwhat its relative power is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.54,0:24:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have\Nbeen able to discern
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.54,0:24:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the direction of the energy\Nof that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.54,0:24:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the direction?\NAnd so these arrows indicate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.54,0:24:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,whether the direction of the field\Nis in a negative direction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.54,0:24:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or a positive direction.\NAnd this of course is extremely important
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.54,0:24:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in the way that we experience things.\NThese things in a negative direction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.54,0:24:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,are experienced as painful,\Nexperienced as suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.54,0:24:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They bring about detriment\Nand destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.54,0:25:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in our lives.\NSo at the bottom for instance
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.95,0:25:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,we have death calibrated at zero.\NAnd you will see that guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.95,0:25:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 30,\Napathy at 50,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.95,0:25:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,grief at 75,\Nfear at 100,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.95,0:25:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,desire, wantingness 125,\Nanger is 150,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.95,0:25:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,pride is 175.\NWhat is amazing happens here
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,at the level of courage\Nthe field which was in a negative direction
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.95,0:25:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,now goes neutral actually\Nat an energy level we calibrate at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.95,0:25:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When we move up to 250\Nthe level called neutral
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.18,0:25:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the field is now\Nin a positive direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.18,0:25:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We then move up to willingness\Nwhich calibrates at 310,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.18,0:25:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,acceptance at 380,\Nlove at 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.18,0:25:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,joy at 540,\Necstasy at 560,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.18,0:25:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the state of infinite serenity and peace\Nand the emotion there
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.18,0:25:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is commonly called bliss.\NThese energy fields influence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.10,0:26:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,our emotions.\NThey are indicators
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.10,0:26:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of a process going on\Nin consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.10,0:26:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They influence how we see\Nand experience the world
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.10,0:26:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and how we experience our relationship\Nto something that is greater
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.10,0:26:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,than our personal self\Nwhich the world calls a deity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.10,0:26:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or for those of you who are not\Naware,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.10,0:26:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a deity is a person\Nwho is in a higher level
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.10,0:26:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to a greater field of consciousness\Nthe powerful fields
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.54,0:26:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which come about on these higher levels.\NThe only reason to review this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.54,0:26:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is so now we can understand\Nwhat happens in our handling
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.67,0:26:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,our technique there of handling\Nacute pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.67,0:26:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We found that resistance to pain\Nresistance to pain
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.67,0:26:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is a negative energy field\Nand if you can use your will power
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.67,0:26:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,against it and resist it\Nwhat you are bringing forth
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.67,0:27:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself\Nis a negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.67,0:27:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrates about 150.\NThis would be about the same level
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.67,0:27:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as the emotions of resentment\Nor grievance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.67,0:27:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotions of grievance\Nwe resent the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.67,0:27:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see\Nwe are angry about the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.63,0:27:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If we move up to letting go resistance\Nif we have the courage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.63,0:27:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if we have the courage\Nto use this technique
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.63,0:27:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,out of our faith and trust\Nin what the doctor is telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.63,0:27:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,about his own personal experience\Nand what he has learned
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.63,0:27:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if we have enough faith in that\Nand we are willing to try it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.82,0:27:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing we can move up to\Nis this level here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.82,0:27:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,at an energy field of 250\Ncalled detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.82,0:27:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving into neutral means\Nnow we are into a positive energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.82,0:27:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that means\NI am willing to experience this thing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.82,0:27:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness moves us up\Nto an energy field of 310
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.82,0:28:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where we say yes\Nto life and its experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.82,0:28:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where we join with it\Nwhere we agree with it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.82,0:28:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where we align with it\Nand where our will expresses itself
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.82,0:28:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,as a positive intention.\NInstead of resisting life then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.27,0:28:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I go with life\Nthat is the wisdom of the Tao
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.27,0:28:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,spelled T-A-O\Nthe wisdom of the Tao
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.27,0:28:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that the willow tree\Nbends with the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.27,0:28:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the oak tree which resists it\Nbreaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.27,0:28:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of resisting\Nwhat has occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.27,0:28:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,once you have barked your shin\Nall you can do is be the willow tree now
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.27,0:28:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and go with that\Nlet go resisting it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.27,0:28:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,allow that experience to flow through you\Nand by doing that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.27,0:28:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you move yourself out of\Na negative painful energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.27,0:28:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,full of resentment and anger and fear\Nwhich is only a negative field of 100
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.27,0:28:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,these are low energy fields\Nthey are a long way from joy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.27,0:29:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the higher the number\Nthe greater the feeling of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.27,0:29:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you can actually choose then\Nand be willing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.27,0:29:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can even accept\Nthat that is what is necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.27,0:29:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle this\Nwhich moves you all the way up to 380
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.17,0:29:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that is a very high energy field\Nso when I choose to go with life
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.17,0:29:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it is running across\Na rattlesnake or whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.17,0:29:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I do\Nwhen I surrender to that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.17,0:29:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then I invite\NI bring forth within myself
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.52,0:29:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a greater power\Na higher energy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.52,0:29:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,those people who are experiencing this technique\Ntherefore end up calling it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a higher power\Nand you will hear people say
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.52,0:29:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I called upon my higher power\Nthose of us who haven't heard that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.52,0:29:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,consider that maybe flaky or far out\Nbecause it is not real to us
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.52,0:29:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so how can we make these experiences real\Nby doing them
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.52,0:29:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,by doing them\Nit is actually through the doingness of it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.52,0:30:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that these things become real\Nby the doing of this exercise then
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.87,0:30:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to experience\Nthat something other than your personal self
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.87,0:30:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is handling this experience\Nand within moments
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.87,0:30:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,what was agonizing\Nis now very bearable
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.87,0:30:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you are out of the fear and the suffering\Nand the resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.87,0:30:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so we want to avoid\Nwe want to bypass a negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.87,0:30:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,a low energy power\Nand we want to move up higher
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.87,0:30:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,why because as we move up to higher energies\Nlove for instance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.87,0:30:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional love\Nis an energy field of 500
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.87,0:30:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when we move into lovingness\Nwhich is an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.22,0:30:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of about 540\Nthe energy field of 540
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.45,0:30:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,has the capacity to heal\Nthose
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.58,0:30:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who are healers\Nwhen we calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.58,0:30:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the field that they generate\Nit is an energy field of 540 and up
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.58,0:31:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it is an immensely loving\Nit is experienced as lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.58,0:31:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotion\Nis experienced as lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.58,0:31:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it is that desire\Nto be with life
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.58,0:31:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to say yes with it\Nto let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.58,0:31:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so acute pain then\Nand the healing
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.58,0:31:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes about automatically\Nfrom this technique
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.58,0:31:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,can be experienced by anyone\NI have done it over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.58,0:31:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone that I have told about it\Nwho has tried it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.58,0:31:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and many people have had the opportunity\NI remember a class on a Sunday night
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.58,0:31:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in which I described the technique\Nand during that week
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.58,0:31:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,several members of the class\Nhad acute injuries
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.58,0:31:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,where this was life saving to them\Nliterally able to carry them through
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.18,0:31:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a terrible experience\Nhow can we then utilize this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.86,0:31:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in our handling of chronic pain\Nchronic pain
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.08,0:31:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is a somewhat different\Nexperience isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.46,0:32:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet one of the aspects\Nof handling it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.46,0:32:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same as we did\Nwith the acute pain
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.42,0:32:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we are going to be doing it\Nwith the chronic pain
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.81,0:32:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in a somewhat different way however\Nas we said
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.90,0:32:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all experience is being experienced\Nin consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.90,0:32:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if you look to see\Nwhere is the pain being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.00,0:32:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's take this thumb\Nyou know just happens to be handy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.00,0:32:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the pain\Nof it being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.19,0:32:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we can say number one\Nthe pain seems to be coming
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.77,0:32:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,from right here\Nthe mind would say well the pain is in
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.37,0:32:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the thumb\Nactually where is the pain being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.91,0:32:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if I go away from the thumb\Nand let's say I move into
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.91,0:32:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the top of my head\Nlet's say I focus on the top of my head
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.91,0:32:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and now from the top of my head\NI look at
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.91,0:33:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,from that space I now experience\Nthe painfulness of the thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.91,0:33:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the painfulness of the thumb\Nhappening
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.33,0:33:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if I do that I begin to notice\Nthat the painfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.33,0:33:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is being experienced everywhere\Nthe painfulness is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.68,0:33:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when you first try this technique\Nyou'll see that the painfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.68,0:33:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is being experienced\Nlike all around your body
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.68,0:33:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all around the energy fields of your body\Nthat it's really going on
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.68,0:33:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of everywhere\Nyou all have the experience of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.68,0:33:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're sick to your stomach\Nand flip floppy and weak in the knees
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.68,0:33:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's being experienced everywhere\Nso if I go into the top of my head
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.80,0:33:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,this is just an exercise\Nthat you do you see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.80,0:33:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and from there I begin to experience\Nthe pain
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.80,0:33:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I then notice that this pain is everywhere\Nand now I use the same technique
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.90,0:33:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that I used\Nin handling the acute pain
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.11,0:34:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I let go resisting\Nwhat is being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.11,0:34:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere\Nit's in no place
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.27,0:34:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is going on\Nand I let go resisting it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.94,0:34:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to review again this technique\Nof letting go resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.94,0:34:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to clearly differentiate\Nthat which is the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.94,0:34:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the sensation, the experience\Nand that which are the thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.02,0:34:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be doing this\Nwith all of life's problems
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.02,0:34:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially with physical illnesses\Nthat there is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.18,0:34:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,an absolute sensation\Ncoming in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.18,0:34:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to what is being experienced\Nand what the mind then does
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.18,0:34:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is elaborate\Nabout that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.18,0:34:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,conceptualize about it\Nlabel it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.18,0:34:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and put concepts on it\Nfor instance you cannot experience
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.41,0:34:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,an ulcer\Nyou cannot experience diabetes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.41,0:35:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you see those are labels\Nthose are concepts
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.44,0:35:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,those are diagnoses\Nwhat are you actually experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.44,0:35:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're actually experiencing\Nlet's say
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.44,0:35:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what the world calls an ulcer\Nis a sensation right here
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.11,0:35:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then your mind says\Nwell if I can't call it ulcer
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.11,0:35:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say it's burning\Nthat again is a concept
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.07,0:35:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we've learned what that means\Nthat's a thought form
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.07,0:35:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which we have learned in our learning\Nactually you're not experiencing a burning
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.07,0:35:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going inside now\Nto an experiencing of the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.07,0:35:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which has no words\Nto the experiencing of the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.07,0:35:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which has no words\Nwhen the animal experiences it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.26,0:35:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it has no words about that\Nit just is with what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.26,0:35:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so we sort of call up\Nour animal nature
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.52,0:35:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and just be with\Nwhat's being experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.52,0:35:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,without saying anything about it\Nwithout elaborating
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.52,0:36:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,why?\Nbecause these thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.52,0:36:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,all bring in programs\Ncomplicated programs
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.52,0:36:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and we then become\Nat the effect of these thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.87,0:36:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,if I say to myself\Nthat I have an ulcer
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.87,0:36:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,then I've got a whole bunch of programs\Nthat go with ulcer
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.87,0:36:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of the nature of mind\NI begin to experience all of that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.87,0:36:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the power of mind\Nand one that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.13,0:36:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,people find most difficult to\Nreally grasp when they
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.13,0:36:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,enter research and\Nwork in the field of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.13,0:36:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is the realization\Nof the power of mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.74,0:36:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,how powerful it is\Nwe just cannot be careless
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.96,0:36:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,about our thoughts\Nonce we understand
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.96,0:36:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of mind and the nature of thought\Nwe begin to realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.18,0:36:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the principles\Nof consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.95,0:37:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is that we are only subject\Nto what we hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.95,0:37:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in this one sentence\Nis
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.56,0:37:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the key to the healing\Nof all illness, pain and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.56,0:37:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we are only subject\Nto what we hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.07,0:37:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind is extraordinarily\Npowerful
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.07,0:37:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the great difficulty\Nthat people have in getting
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.07,0:37:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is how powerful the mind is\Nand therefore in dealing with pain
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.65,0:37:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or with suffering of any kind\Nthe first thing we have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.42,0:37:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is discontinue\Nlet go of and cancel
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.42,0:37:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all of our belief systems\Nabout that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.42,0:37:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it is\Nas the research has shown
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.42,0:37:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the belief system itself\Nthat literally creates
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.67,0:37:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience\Nthe incident is an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.67,0:37:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of that belief system\Nit is like the mind justifying
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.67,0:38:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that what it believes is true\Nwe can find out whether
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.89,0:38:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,this is so or not our self\Nby beginning to cancel it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.89,0:38:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to cancel as we said\Nat the beginning of this film
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.89,0:38:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the belief that pain and suffering\Nare the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.72,0:38:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to cancel\Nall thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.72,0:38:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and all thoughts\Nare really belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.72,0:38:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead we have to go\Nfor radical truth
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.72,0:38:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,radical in that we drop off\Neverything except
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.72,0:38:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencing\Nof what is literally
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.01,0:38:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,being experienced\Nand letting go the resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.42,0:38:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to that\Nwhen we do
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.42,0:38:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we will experience a relief\Nof the suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.65,0:38:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and curiously enough\Nwe will reach a point
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.65,0:38:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,where we don't care\Nwhether the pain is there or not
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.45,0:39:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that may be a difficult thing\Nto conceive of in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.64,0:39:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because the mind wants to be\Nrid of the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.06,0:39:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,our whole approach instead\Nis to accept it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.31,0:39:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to accept it\Nto let the pain be there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.31,0:39:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but to move away from it\Nin other words it is like the pain is here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.31,0:39:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you experience the morphine\Nthe pain of the broken ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.31,0:39:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say is there\Nand then you begin to feel yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.31,0:39:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,move away from that pain\Nit's no longer you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.31,0:39:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's no longer yours\Nin this case the narcotic does
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.31,0:39:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what we are explaining\Ncan be done by consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.31,0:39:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,actually the narcotic\Nactually doesn't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.31,0:39:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the narcotic enables\Nour consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.44,0:39:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to make this very move\Nand we can learn to make
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.44,0:39:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,this very move\Nwithout being triggered
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.44,0:39:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,by a narcotic\NI have had to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.44,0:40:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself have been allergic\Nseverely allergic
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.89,0:40:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to any kind of analgesic\Nor narcotic or anesthetic
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.89,0:40:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for well over 20 years\Nand over those 22 years
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.89,0:40:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have had all kinds of\Nsevere illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.89,0:40:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and accidents etc\Nand so of necessity
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.89,0:40:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the usual measures\NI have had to investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.89,0:40:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the capacity\Nwhat is the power of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.89,0:40:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw that all\Nthat the analgesic did
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.89,0:40:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,was allow consciousness\Nto exercise its own power
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.89,0:40:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore we can own\Nthat we have that power
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.89,0:40:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,within our own consciousness\Nto achieve the same result
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.59,0:40:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,without the analgesic\Nwe begin to move away from it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.59,0:40:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,by letting go resisting it\Nlet the pain be there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.59,0:40:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and what we are going to do\Nis shift our way of being
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.59,0:40:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with that pain\Nwe are going to shift our way
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.59,0:41:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of being with it\Nto the point that we don't care
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.59,0:41:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it is there or not\Ndoes that sound amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.66,0:41:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that you don't even care\Nwhether it is there or not
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.66,0:41:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it is very simple\Nmany things in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.66,0:41:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you have been upset over\Nyou know what I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.55,0:41:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,some place in your backyard\Nthat was driving you crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.55,0:41:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and one day you say\Noh the heck with it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.55,0:41:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly you move right\Nyou see on this field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.06,0:41:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you move here from\Ntrying to do something about it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.06,0:41:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and control it\Nand change it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.10,0:41:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and exert your will\Nsee when you try to change others
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.10,0:41:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or you try to change people\Nplaces and circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.10,0:41:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute you let it be there\Nyou like disappear your experience of it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.10,0:41:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you move all the way up to here\Nand we are going to show you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.10,0:42:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time we end the film\Nhow to move all the way up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.10,0:42:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to a state of painlessness\Na state of painlessness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.10,0:42:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in the presence of pain\Nthe experience of that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.91,0:42:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the sensations\Ncoming from
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.01,0:42:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say a painful injury\Nare going on
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.46,0:42:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and who cares about it\Nthe sensations from this amputation
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.97,0:42:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,which I only did a few months ago\Nare going on
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.99,0:42:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't care about it\Nit makes no difference
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.99,0:42:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,if they are there, they are there\Nand if they are not, they are not
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.66,0:42:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that all comes about\Nthrough that very simple practice
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.66,0:42:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,very simple practice\Nin which you are totally indifferent
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.66,0:42:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the time\Nthe pain that I have experienced in my own life
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.66,0:42:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and other people who have used this technique\Neventually the pain disappears of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.95,0:42:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes in the case of an acute injury\Nor it may take months
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.95,0:43:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I had one illness that took\Nwell over a year
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.66,0:43:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of constantly letting go\Nconstantly releasing, constantly surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.66,0:43:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,before it finally disappeared\Nso I know that the sensations
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.66,0:43:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,will eventually die out\Nbut I am not doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.66,0:43:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to achieve that\Nyou see that would be trying to change it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.66,0:43:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying to get rid of it\Nbut I do know as a matter of clinical observation
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.78,0:43:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that as you let go resisting it\Nyou come to a point
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.78,0:43:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,where you don't care whether it is there or not\Nand then suddenly one morning
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.78,0:43:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you wake up and it is gone\Nbut we don't let go resisting it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.23,0:43:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to get rid of the pain\Nthat is a happy side effect
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.23,0:43:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,when you reach the point\Nwhere you don't care whether it is there or not
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.23,0:43:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,then what difference does it make\Nwhether it continues it or not
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.23,0:43:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because at that point\Nyou are like immune to the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.16,0:43:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a very good thing to know\Nthat your mind has this power
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.16,0:44:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and all you need is somebody\Nto point it out to you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.16,0:44:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and encourage you to try it\Nand you will see that it works
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.16,0:44:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no need to be\Nin a state of suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.16,0:44:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,over pain of any kind\Npain is one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.54,0:44:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering is another\Nyou have to say that over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.58,0:44:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to yourself\Nand begin to utilize these techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.58,0:44:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you will experience a separation\Nwhere there is you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.58,0:44:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there is the pain\Nyou are not connected with it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.58,0:44:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you are something over greater\Nthan and beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.58,0:44:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is painful\Nand no longer suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.58,0:44:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,how to handle the acute situation\Nhow to handle the chronic situation
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.20,0:44:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that leads us into the subject\Nof how to be with it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.20,0:44:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,how to be with it\Nlife's experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.78,0:44:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the meaning of them\Nwhat is the meaning of them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.78,0:44:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is how you experience them\Nhow you feel about them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.78,0:45:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't make any difference at all\Nwhat happens in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.87,0:45:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can be with it\Nin a certain way
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.87,0:45:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so it isn't what's happening out there\Nit's how you are with it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.87,0:45:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,people who are quite evolved\Ncan be with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.87,0:45:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,situations that look\Ndramatically tragic
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.87,0:45:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and be unaffected by them\Nand how is that so
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.90,0:45:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because they begin to become aware\Nof who they are
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.90,0:45:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and so\None of the things that we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.90,0:45:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,about pain\Nis consciously progress
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the movement and growth\Nof our own consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.80,0:45:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,pain proneness comes about\Nas a result of holding
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.80,0:45:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of negative kinds of thoughts\Nand feelings within us
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.09,0:45:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so that general spiritual work\Ngeneral work in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.12,0:45:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,then has an overall value\Nthe more
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.79,0:46:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance\Nwe forgive ourselves and others
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.79,0:46:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a process\Nof forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.79,0:46:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which was not really heard about much\Nexcept in religion
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.79,0:46:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and has now become\Nalmost a social phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.86,0:46:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,now when you go about in your social life\Nand somebody brings up a resentment
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.86,0:46:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the other people will look at them\Nbecause they know the next step
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.86,0:46:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is this person has to learn\Nhow to forgive that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.86,0:46:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or they are going to be at the painful effect of that\Nso we find that all pain and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.53,0:46:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,comes about\Nthat which we are already holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.53,0:46:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,why are some people\Nso susceptible
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.53,0:46:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to pain and suffering\Nand other people it is very transitory
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.53,0:46:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain and the suffering goes\Nthrough the surface of them
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.53,0:46:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but not into the core of them\Nso that you can get extremely upset
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.59,0:46:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,over something\Nbut that who you are within
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.59,0:46:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,remains unruffled\Nsomehow there has been a differentiation
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.59,0:47:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of who I am\Nfrom the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.59,0:47:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain is totally unruffled\Nand allows the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.59,0:47:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to flow through me\Nand upset
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.52,0:47:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the upset lasts for hours\Nthe emotional conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.52,0:47:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it happens to be\Nbut that which is within
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.52,0:47:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is myself\Ndoes not even participate in that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.62,0:47:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that beginning differentiation\Nof what is my real self
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.62,0:47:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,from what is experience\Nletting go of the habit
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.62,0:47:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of identifying that I am experience\Nthat something is happening
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.62,0:47:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am not the experience\Nhow can we bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.84,0:47:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this evolution and this growth in our self\Nthat takes us back
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.90,0:47:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to the scale of consciousness\Nthat we have here
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.90,0:47:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and as we look at it\Nwe will see how to be with chronic pain
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.90,0:47:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we can transcend it\Nand no longer be
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.90,0:48:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state of suffering\Nabout it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.22,0:48:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you remember at the bottom of the chart\Nwe said guilt has a negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.22,0:48:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,which we calibrate at 30\Ndeath is zero
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.22,0:48:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so prolonged and excessive guilt\Nfor instance
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.22,0:48:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,makes us prone to sickness\Naccident, injury, pain and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.22,0:48:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we see that the view of the world\Nthe view of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.22,0:48:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes out of this guiltiness\Nwhich is a constant habit
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.22,0:48:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of sin and suffering\Nwe see that it brings about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.22,0:48:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,self-hatred\Nand we see that the process
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.22,0:48:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in consciousness is one of\Ndestruction
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.22,0:48:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,self-destruction out of this self-hatredness\Nso one of the belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.31,0:48:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to give up\Nis that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.31,0:48:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt and suffering\Nhave any particular value
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.31,0:48:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as we look at this\Nwhere we see
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.38,0:48:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as we go up the energy fields\Nwhere we see
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.38,0:49:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that those who are approaching\Nthe energy fields of the saints
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.38,0:49:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the great beings\Nthe closer you get to God
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.38,0:49:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and suffering\Nas you experience the ultimate reality
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.34,0:49:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you go through the doors\Nof a progressive lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.34,0:49:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because love increases and expands\Nas you go up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.34,0:49:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,through joy, through ecstasy\Nto a state of infinite peace
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.34,0:49:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha or the Christ\Nor the great saints
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.34,0:49:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or the enlightened beings of the planet\Ndo not get there through guilt and pain and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.53,0:49:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they go there through joy\Nso we have to give up worshipping
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.91,0:49:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the God of suffering\Nwe have to give up worshipping
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.91,0:49:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,for those of you who are Christians\Nwe have to give up worshipping
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.91,0:49:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the God of the crucifixion\Nthe Christ of the crucifixion
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.91,0:49:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and move on to the Christ\Nof the resurrection
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.91,0:49:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the message was not that of death\Nand sin and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.91,0:49:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,people who identify themselves as a body\Nthe strict materialist
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.91,0:50:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at the Christ on the cross\Nas a body
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.91,0:50:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and came out with pain, sin\Nguilt and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.10,0:50:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,was that the message?\Nis that what Christ died for
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.10,0:50:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to teach everybody\Nthat we are a physical body
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.23,0:50:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,or was his message the direct opposite\Nhis message was the direct opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.23,0:50:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are not limited\Nthat we are not that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.23,0:50:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we have to substitute\Nour confused ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.23,0:50:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to look at\Nmoving towards
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.23,0:50:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a lovingness\Nto a higher state of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.23,0:50:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to get what the message was\Nthe Christ of the resurrection
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.00,0:50:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have to give up\Nthat penance, guilt and sin
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.00,0:50:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and suffering\Nare somehow of enormous spiritual benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.00,0:50:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,frankly\Nall the hundreds and thousands of people
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.00,0:50:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've clinically treated\Nover 35 years
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.00,0:51:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,who had chronic pain, guilt\Nsin and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.45,0:51:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,were the most selfish and self-centered persons\NI had ever met
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.02,0:51:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,chronic pain and suffering\Ndoes not make you an enlightened loving being
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.02,0:51:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes you usually cranky\Nhorrible
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.09,0:51:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,selfish, self-centered\Nand brings you up to the next level
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.09,0:51:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of\Nself-pity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.09,0:51:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,most people with chronic pain\Nare into self-pity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.09,0:51:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they are into grief\Nthey are into poor me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.09,0:51:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they are into the endless fear\Nof the continuation of their state
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.09,0:51:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether it's going to get worse\Nthey're constantly resisting it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.09,0:51:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire to get away from it\Nthese are all negative energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.09,0:51:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they are very very angry\Nthe anger of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.09,0:51:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in chronic pain is enormous\Nthey are stuck in it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.09,0:51:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and they are very proud of the fact\Nthat nobody has been able
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.09,0:51:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to help them with this\Nand they will tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.09,0:52:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the doctors they went to\Nand all the treatments they had
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.09,0:52:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and how all of those things didn't work\Nwe want to move up to the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.18,0:52:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,courage, the capacity\Nthe fact that something can be done
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.18,0:52:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,about the way we can be\Nwith this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.24,0:52:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the way that we can be with it\Nby using our simple
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.24,0:52:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,letting go resisting\Ntechnique
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.24,0:52:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,our willingness to do that\Nare we willing to try something
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.24,0:52:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,do we have the courage to try it\Nto let go resisting it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.24,0:52:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and end up at least detached\Nto at least move out of this
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.24,0:52:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,state of suffering\Nyou see these energy fields are negative
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.24,0:52:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we move up to an energy field\Nup around here you see
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.37,0:52:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that the needle swings to the right\Nit means these are states of less and less
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.37,0:52:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering as we move up into joy\Nso how can I be
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.37,0:52:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with that chronic condition\Ncan I be willing to be with that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.37,0:52:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,can I let go resisting it\Ncan I begin to differentiate
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.37,0:53:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am that which is with it\Nhow to be with that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.37,0:53:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,can I accept that\Ncan I accept
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.50,0:53:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,my capacity to be with it\Nin a state of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.20,0:53:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,non suffering\Nwe see that the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.23,0:53:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we look at the emotions that go with these\Nparticular energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.23,0:53:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and we see the emotions\Nthat go with chronic pain
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.42,0:53:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we see self hatred\Nthe feeling that one is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.42,0:53:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a victim\Nthe self hatred of the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.42,0:53:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we see the process going on in consciousness\Nthere is a destructive one
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.42,0:53:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we see the hopelessness\Nnothing can be done about my condition
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.42,0:53:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what we said about\Nthe nature of the power of mind is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.94,0:53:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you hold that in mind\Nyou literally create that as your experience
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.94,0:53:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who\Nsays my condition
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.94,0:53:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is hopeless\Nthen creates for themself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.94,0:54:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a condition which is hopeless\Nand resistive to treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.22,0:54:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we see the\Nperson in grief
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.22,0:54:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we move them up into apathy into grief\Nthat they are in a constant state of regret
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.22,0:54:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a feeling of loss\Na feeling of despondency
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.26,0:54:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,these are feelings which are only human\Nthese are not feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.26,0:54:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that we want to feel guilty about\Nthese are feelings we want to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.26,0:54:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,through understanding\Nthey become resolved
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.02,0:54:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,when I recently cut this thumb off\NI went through all of these
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.02,0:54:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,first the feeling I was being punished somehow\Nattacked by the forces of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.02,0:54:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,retribution or something\Nthe pain was acute
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.22,0:54:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I looked at it and I felt hopeless\Ninto despair
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.22,0:54:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and replaced etc\Nand I went into grief
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.22,0:54:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and mourning\Nyou know grieving and mourning
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.22,0:54:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as though you had lost a loved one\Na fear of the consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.44,0:55:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a fear that this pain and suffering\Nwas going to continue and go on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.44,0:55:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt myself resisting\Nthe desire to get away from
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.44,0:55:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the injury the disability\Nthe pain the suffering the surgery whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.44,0:55:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and feeling angry\Nangry at life angry at fate
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.44,0:55:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,angry at myself\NI felt I was only very human
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.44,0:55:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and then moving into pride\Nthat I was going to do something about it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.44,0:55:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and the courage to begin to look at\Nwhat are the techniques that I know work
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.44,0:55:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in this kind of a circumstance\Nand the willingness to begin utilizing them
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.44,0:55:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin letting go\Nresisting and using that technique
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.44,0:55:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually moving up\Ninto the acceptance of it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.44,0:55:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so that if it's there\Nit's ok if it's there
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.44,0:55:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's not there\Nit's ok if it's not there
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.44,0:55:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the field here\Nthere's one in which we say
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.54,0:55:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,yes it's ok either way\Nit's ok
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.60,0:55:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're totally released\Nfrom our resistance to the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.60,0:56:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't care if it's there\Nif it's there it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.60,0:56:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's not there that's fine too\Nthe willingness to be forgiving
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.60,0:56:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and we want to move eventually\Ninto compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.60,0:56:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that acceptance of the human condition\Nand of the human experience
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.60,0:56:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,without being resentful about it\Nwithout feeling pity
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.60,0:56:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,without being angry\Nwithout being prideful
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.60,0:56:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and going into a make wrong\Nwithout attacking ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.40,0:56:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how can we move up to an energy field\Ncalled love or even joy
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.66,0:56:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in that I can only go back to my own experience\Nmy own personal experience
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.66,0:56:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is possible\Nwhat is possible
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.66,0:56:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,when somebody shares with us their experience\Nthen we learn what is possible
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.69,0:56:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in human consciousness\Nas I move through this experience
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.49,0:56:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened was\NI began to call on
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.49,0:56:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,some power greater than myself\NI kept surrendering it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.49,0:56:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,turning it over\NI remember I went to the emergency room
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.49,0:57:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to inform them\NI couldn't take anesthesia
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.49,0:57:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or analgesia of any kind\Nand so the surgeon was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.62,0:57:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhat perplexed about\Nhow this was going to be handled
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.74,0:57:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said I have my own ways\NI have my own ways
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.84,0:57:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and to make him feel better\NI had a self hypnotic technique
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.84,0:57:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and this would make\Nso anyway he relaxed
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.84,0:57:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling that it was being handled\Nand what I did then was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.45,0:57:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I went in with inside myself\Nand I released and let go
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.70,0:57:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go resisting\Nand I called upon
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.74,0:57:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the God of my own understanding\Nthat aspect of one's greater self
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.99,0:57:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't need to believe in God\Nbut we can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.99,0:57:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is some energy field\Ngreater than our personal self
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.99,0:57:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which has unlimited power\Nand so what I did
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.41,0:57:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is by constantly surrendering\Nand let's face it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.41,0:58:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're in a situation like that\Noverwhelmed by excruciating pain
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.41,0:58:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and suffering\Nall the props are pulled out
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.41,0:58:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean this is when you really come up\Nwith what you really believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.41,0:58:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is a great opportunity\Nand so as I let go
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.86,0:58:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering\Nand let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.86,0:58:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly it was as though\NI was lifted out of my body
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.86,0:58:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I came into a state of profound inner peace\Nan incredible state
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.86,0:58:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of stillness\Nexquisite inner serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.86,0:58:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and joy\Nand I realized that something
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.27,0:58:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,other than my personal self\Nwas handling this experience
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.27,0:58:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,something other than the personal David\Nwas handling the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.27,0:58:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and so this is something\Nwe've learned to do
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.56,0:58:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with chronic pain\Nto surrender it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.56,0:58:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to one's personal God\Nto whatever one believes in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.56,0:59:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle the pain for us\Nwhat happens when we do this
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.98,0:59:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the experience of\Nsomething greater than
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.98,0:59:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,one's personal self\Nhandles that pain
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.06,0:59:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that was my personal experience\Nthat some great energy
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.06,0:59:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,came in\Nand that great energy
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.06,0:59:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you can call it a great energy\Nbecause you can verify the existence
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.06,0:59:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of that great energy\Nthis great energy
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.06,0:59:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,handled it for me\Nit's like I said
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.42,0:59:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God I can't do it\Nyou do it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.45,0:59:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I turned my burden over\Nand allowed that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.45,0:59:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which is in the universe\Nto handle it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.31,0:59:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for those of you\Nto whom this seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.31,0:59:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps an outlandish experience\Nlet's look at it then
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.60,0:59:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,from a level that would be understandable\Nif you're in a state of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.60,0:59:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,550 where healing begins to take place\Nwithin the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.70,1:00:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there is the release of endorphins\Nin other words
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.70,1:00:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain within itself\Nfrom this energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.70,1:00:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to release endorphins\Nendorphins are those
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.24,1:00:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,things released by narcotics\Nit isn't the narcotic at all
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.24,1:00:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that has the effect on the brain\Nbut the fact that the narcotic releases
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.24,1:00:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,these so called opioids\Nthat are released
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.24,1:00:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the endorphins within the brain\Nand so therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.85,1:00:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,subsequent to the experience\NI was aware that within me
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.85,1:00:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there was something\Nthat was handling the pain for me
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.85,1:00:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically\Nit didn't involve my personal self at all
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.88,1:00:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and as the\Nintensity of the pain would increase
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.88,1:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that within me\Nthat energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.88,1:00:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which expresses itself\Non the physical plane
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.88,1:00:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through the release of these endorphins\Nautomatically handling the pain
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.88,1:01:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when we calibrated\Nthe energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.81,1:01:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of that power\Nwithin our self
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.81,1:01:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which is automatically handling the pain\Nwe calibrated
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.81,1:01:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,an energy field at 750\Nwithin us
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.22,1:01:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is the capacity\Nof letting go our smallness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.29,1:01:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say this is all our smallness\Nand summoning forth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.32,1:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is already\Npresent and within us
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.32,1:01:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,a powerful energy field\Nof a plus 750
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.45,1:01:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that energy field has the power\Nto handle the pain
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.45,1:01:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain and the suffering\Nwas completely and totally relieved
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.96,1:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was instead\Na state of infinite inner serenity
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.96,1:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and peace\Nthat inner serenity and peace
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.06,1:01:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,stays within\Nin a permanent kind of a basis
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.06,1:01:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,those are ways\Nto be with that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.54,1:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,ways to be with that\Nand how can we
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.43,1:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,augment our\Nendeavors in these directions
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.43,1:02:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because certainly\Nspiritual work
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.43,1:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,work in consciousness\Nwe can do it acutely
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.43,1:02:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but those processes\Nsuch as forgiveness and all
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.43,1:02:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,take a period of time\Nin the meantime
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.55,1:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what can we do\Nwhat about such
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.55,1:02:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,ancillary procedures\Nas acupuncture and hypnosis
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.55,1:02:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we know that acupuncture\Ncan be extremely effective
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.54,1:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there is certainly nothing wrong\Nwe said that all illnesses
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.54,1:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,all pain suffering forms\Nare physical mental and spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.54,1:02:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I just described to you\Nhow it's handled from the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.80,1:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,before that we described\Nhow it is handled on the level of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.80,1:02:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness itself\Nthrough the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.22,1:02:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and certainly at the same time\Nwe want to do what we can physically
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.41,1:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,acupuncture in my own experience\Nextremely effective
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.41,1:03:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself had an ulcer\Nfor some 20 or 25 years
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.41,1:03:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it was intractable and incurable\NI had every treatment
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.41,1:03:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,known to medical science\Nit was only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.41,1:03:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,before we would have to have\Na subtotal gastrectomy
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.41,1:03:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and reparative gastrointestinal surgery\Nwhich is a major procedure
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.41,1:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,let me tell you\Nand so I tried acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.70,1:03:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and frankly by the third treatment\Nthe pain and suffering left
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.70,1:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so I know myself that these\Nare very very effective
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.70,1:03:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would certainly add acupuncture\Nfor chronic intractable pain
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.70,1:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it certainly is one of the things\Nthat we want to try
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.70,1:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,we know that the reliance on analgesics\Nhas two negative effects
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.95,1:03:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,one is because it is such a\Nmagical short term solution
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.95,1:03:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you never grow in consciousness\Nyou feel that the power
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.95,1:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you give away your power to this pill\Nthe power which is really
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.95,1:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that of your own consciousness\Nyou give it to the pill
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.95,1:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and you stop your own growth\Nso that's one negative effect
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.95,1:04:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the other of course is the progressive dependency\Non the analgesics and the narcotics
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.95,1:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,which create and compounds\Nthe whole problem now
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.95,1:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with a problem that may be more severe\Nthan the one you started with
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.62,1:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so what other techniques are available to us\Nlet's talk a little bit about hypnosis
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.62,1:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly a great deal\Nis known about hypnosis now
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.62,1:04:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it once was a subject\Nthat medicine avoided
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.62,1:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but now medicine is very interested\Nin acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.62,1:04:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and hypnosis\Nwhat kind of hypnotic techniques
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.62,1:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the place of these\Nin the healing of chronic pain
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.68,1:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,first thing we need to know\Nis that the only form of hypnosis
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.68,1:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that is really acceptable\Nis that of self hypnosis
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.68,1:04:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not advisable\Nfor reasons having to do with consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.68,1:05:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and for other reasons\Nthat we can't go into in this tape
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.68,1:05:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it is inadvisable\Nto seek hypnosis from another
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.68,1:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but to learn it from yourself\Nand what do you do once you learn it
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.97,1:05:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,once you learn this technique\Nand we will describe in the next few minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.97,1:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly how to do it\Nit is extremely simple
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.86,1:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you can use the hypnotic state\Nwhich is really only a state
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.86,1:05:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of high suggestibility\Nto learn the very things
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.86,1:05:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we have been talking about today\Nif you put yourself in an extremely relaxed state
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.86,1:05:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to experiment\Nand experience out
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.86,1:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of what we have been talking about today\Nthe learning is much faster
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.86,1:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the value of self hypnosis\Nin my experience is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.79,1:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that it enables you\Nto reach a level of concentration
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.18,1:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that you wouldn't be able to reach otherwise\Nthat is really its value
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.18,1:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in that suggestible state\Nyou are capable of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.50,1:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,degrees of concentration\Nthat you aren't ordinarily capable of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.50,1:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are too distracted\Nby what is going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.98,1:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so what is a very simple technique\Nthat you can utilize
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.98,1:06:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think anybody\Nwho has any chronic physical condition
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.98,1:06:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,should really learn how to do this\Nit is extremely simple
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.62,1:06:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you just sit down in a very relaxed state\Nand what you are going to do now
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.87,1:06:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is progressively relax yourself\Nso instead of the word hypnosis
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.87,1:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,which has all kinds of stage\Nstage meanings
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.87,1:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and occult meanings\Nforget all that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.87,1:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we are going to talk now\Nabout extreme relaxation
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.87,1:06:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and a state of heightened suggestibility\Nand the capacity to concentrate
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.87,1:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we can do this\Nwith a very simple technique
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.00,1:06:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of counting from 1 to 10\Nwe sit down
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.35,1:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we lie down in a very comfortable position\Nand we start out
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.45,1:07:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,by saying to ourselves\Nnumber 1
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.70,1:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that announces to us\Nthat we are about to do this procedure
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.02,1:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we then go into number 2\Nyou can picture yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.02,1:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in 10 steps\Nthe first step
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.06,1:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you are initiating the experience\Nin the next step
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.06,1:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what you do is\Nyou allow yourself some time
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.06,1:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to relax all the muscles in your head\Nall the muscles
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.06,1:07:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and you notice as you do that\Nthe soreness in your face muscles
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.06,1:07:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and your jaw muscles\Nthe tension of the day
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.06,1:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,your cheeks are actually sore\Njust poke right here now
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.06,1:07:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as you watch me and you will see\Nthat you are in 10 all day long
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.86,1:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so you allow yourself several minutes\Nto relax the head
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.86,1:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you move on to number 3\Nwhere you relax your neck
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.86,1:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you relax all those tensions in your neck\Nand your upper shoulders
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.98,1:07:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you move into number 4\Nwhere you say to yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.05,1:08:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,focus 4\Nyou move and you relax your back
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.05,1:08:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and your chest muscles\Nand number 5
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.05,1:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you just progressively relax\Nstarting with the biggest muscles
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.05,1:08:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the upper arms and the lower arms\Nand the fingers and the hands
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.27,1:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,number 6\Nyou allow your chest and your torso to relax
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.27,1:08:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,number 7\Nyou move into the lower abdomen
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.37,1:08:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,relaxing all the tensions\Nthat you have been holding in your belly
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.82,1:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and your guts\Nnumber 8
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.82,1:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you move into the hips and the buttocks\Nand the general regions
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.82,1:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and allow all those relaxations\Nnumber 9
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.82,1:08:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you allow that to flow down your legs\Nnow you tell yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.82,1:08:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in focus 10\Nand you use that letting go resistance
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.62,1:08:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,which we have been talking about\Nthroughout this
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.62,1:08:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,visit today\Nallowing yourself to let go
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.62,1:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all resistance to this profound\Nstate of relaxation
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.90,1:09:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and in this profound state of relaxation\Nyou now tell yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.90,1:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the things you want to know\Nand let go resisting them
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.90,1:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,let go resisting the thought\Nthat pain
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.90,1:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is something\Nand suffering is something else
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.13,1:09:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such thing\Nas suffering in pain
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.13,1:09:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when that pain is not resisted\Nin that profoundly relaxed state
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.48,1:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,now you let go resisting\Nthe pain
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.63,1:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is going to be used\Nfor a chronic pain condition
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.63,1:09:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you are going to go back to the things we said\Nnotice that the pain is everywhere
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.63,1:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,notice that you can let go your resistance\Nto that pain
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.05,1:09:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,notice that you can like open the door\Nthat you can let it happen
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.78,1:09:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,without it affecting\Nthat which you really are
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.78,1:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in it you can begin\Nto move yourself up through these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.82,1:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as we described before\Nyou can move yourself up
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.82,1:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to a lovingness for yourself\Na compassion
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.82,1:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for your beauty as a human being\Nwe said it about an energy
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.58,1:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,field of 540 to 550\Nthis lovingness comes forth
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.58,1:10:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you know when that has happened\Nit has happened when you can
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.87,1:10:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,become light hearted about it\Nwhen you can laugh at yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.87,1:10:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you see I tell everybody\Nthey say you lost your thumb
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.87,1:10:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that is right I can only count up to 9\Nyou can only count up to 9 now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.87,1:10:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so your capacity to laugh at yourself\Nhumor
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.87,1:10:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we got the energy field of humor\Nis at about 550
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.87,1:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,humor heals\Nand certainly there has been books out recently
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.00,1:10:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by people who are celebrities\Nwho are well known
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.00,1:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who have healed physical illnesses\Nthe use of laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.00,1:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and so laughter\Nthe choosing of laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.00,1:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the choosing of humor\Nputting yourself in a loving
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.00,1:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,laughing energy field\Nwhich tends to heal of its own nature
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.00,1:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we know that an energy field\Na positive energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.00,1:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of 550\Nthe capacity now to laugh at that misfortune
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.06,1:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what does that do for you\Nit means that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.06,1:11:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience is one thing\Nand that which I am in truth
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.06,1:11:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is something else\NI am not that experience
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.06,1:11:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you see I am not at the effect of that\NI am no longer victim
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.06,1:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have stopped struggling with it\NI have stopped resisting
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.06,1:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you notice that as you go through\Nacceptance and willingness
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.06,1:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and through neutral\Nyou become released from that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.26,1:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and what does that mean\Nyou see when you are resisting it
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.26,1:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying to get away from it\Nyou are down here
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.26,1:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see the process is one of entrapment\Nand suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.26,1:11:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as I resist the pain\Nso long as I am angry
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.26,1:11:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and grit my teeth\Nand struggle against it
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.26,1:12:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to force my will\NI become further enmeshed
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.26,1:12:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like the quagmire\Nthe more I struggle
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.54,1:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the more entrapped I become\Nthe being let go of going free
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.54,1:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,see this energy field over here\Nis one of freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.61,1:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as we go into freedom\Nmeans to be released from that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.61,1:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the courage to face this issue\Nand do something about it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.61,1:12:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,empowers me\Nmy willingness moves me up
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.61,1:12:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,through a transformation of consciousness\Ninto my willingness to be forgiving
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.61,1:12:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and loving and compassionate\Nand through my own experience
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.61,1:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,one can transcend it\Nliterally move beyond that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.61,1:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,identification with the body\Nand what has happened to it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.61,1:12:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,into a conscious awareness\Nthat one is something other than the body
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.47,1:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,when we talk about health\None other visit that we'll have
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.47,1:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,about this series\Nwe'll talk about the body being in such a state
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.47,1:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that one is hardly even aware\Nof its existence
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.50,1:13:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that everything is so harmonious\Nthe letting go of resistance
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.50,1:13:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,has been so complete\Nthat there is hardly any awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.50,1:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body is even there\Nthis also happens with pain
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.54,1:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the thought\Nthe memory
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.54,1:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness\Nthat there is some pain there
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.54,1:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,only happens for a few fleeting seconds\Nduring the day
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.82,1:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,although this happened a few months ago\NI use this example of the thumb
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.82,1:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,only as an example of the realness\Nof what I'm talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.92,1:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it only comes to me a couple seconds\Nthroughout the day now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.92,1:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is pain still there\Nafter I'm up about an hour
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.92,1:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly I'll notice the thumb\Nand I'll say, oh
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.92,1:13:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like I'm not even aware of its presence\Nmaybe a few other times
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.50,1:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the daytime\Nthat I experience in a 24 hour period
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.50,1:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,now\Nwith this which is still
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.50,1:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as the world would say, painful\Nis literally amounts to
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.50,1:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,probably a few seconds\Nmaybe 5 or 10 seconds in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.88,1:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe a few seconds in the afternoon\Nthe totality of suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.88,1:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of this experience\Nwhich is only a couple months old
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.88,1:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and for an amputation that's not a long period of time\Namounts to probably less than 30 seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.88,1:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,can all do it\Nbecause through doing it we realize
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.88,1:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who we really are
